# Runtime Module

## Overview

Checkpoint & Durability system enables long-running flows to survive crashes and resume without context loss

## Goals

- **G1** — Checkpoint & Durability system enables long-running flows to survive crashes and resume without context loss
- **G2** — Token Budgeting tracks and enforces per-step spend with cost analytics visible in Agents view
- **G3** — Boss-first execution: GSD mode runs autonomously with optional Check mode for gate review

## Key Architecture Decisions

_No architecture decisions documented yet._

## Key Designs

- **D1** — Runtime Infrastructure

## Module Dependencies

Depends on: [cli](cli/module.ad), [provider](provider/module.ad), [relay](relay/module.ad)

